name: Half-assed LoRAs vol. 3
description:
This is a collection of LoRAs that I didn't want to show up as separate posts. This may be due to the quality that does not fit my standards overall, or due to a strong burnout, instability, etc.

However, someone may find something useful in this collection, this is why I am sharing it with the community.

The base model is Suzumehachi.
